Dialogs.Dialog: You want to go for it？
Do you take a lot of pictures？ Hmm？
I'm not used to this kind of thing...
Are we done yet？ We'll continue another time.
I'm glad I was able to take so many pictures.
Well, that's it for this time. We got quite a lot of shots, didn't we？
I guess so. I got a lot of shots, so I'll stop here.
Did you take that many pictures？
I got carried away and took too many pictures.
You could have taken more photos, though.
Huh, you've finished taking photos already？
I got quite a few shots, so I'm happy with that. Thank you.
Enough is enough, right？ I'm done for the day.
I understand. I don't want you to get tired, ▲小早川＊▲.
Did you get a good photo？
Maybe. Keep looking forward to it.
Hehe, I was just getting into it.
Oh, sorry. Let's just get this over with.
I took quite a few photos before I knew it.
It looks like you got some good photos.
I might have been pretty nervous.
I guess I was too eager.
Aren't you taking a little too many photos？
Stop taking pictures all the time, come on...
Hey, photos are nice, but come on... listen to me.
Okay, I'm done with the pictures.
You know, why don't you stop taking photos all the time？
Hey... enough photos. We have other fun things to do.
Make sure you get a clean shot, okay？
Take a cute picture of me, okay？ Hehe.
Please give me the best angle.
You don't have a problem with the model, do you？
I might be interested to see how the photos turn out.
Make sure you take good photos, because I'm looking forward to it.
I always look forward to having the photos taken.
Let's make a lot of memories together.
This moment is a memory, too.
Let's keep adding more and more photos.
Will we remember this photos in the future？
I won't let you take that kind of picture.
Take the best picture you can, okay？
If it's not a pretty photo, I won't look at it.
I get excited when I see the finished photos.
In spite of this, I'm looking forward to it.
It's fun for both of us to look at the finished photos together.
What kind of photos will they be？
Little by little, our memories grow.
These are all memories, and we must cherish them.
How much more memories can we add？
I wish I could make many more memories.
Hah,I don't know what you are getting on about.
Of course you can't do that.
It's going to be all red faced photos...
Don't look at me all the time.
I don't want to be told how difficult it is.
You were looking at me in a wrong way...
It's going to take some good photos.
You look good like this, ▲小早川＊▲.
I like your expression right now.
I'll have to get more creative with how I take photos.
I wish you could bring out a more natural look.
Maybe we're both getting used to the camera.
I knew it. It's so cute.
It would be nice to have a different expression from usual.
I'm getting the hang of it.
What's wrong with me being nervous...
I wonder if I can take a good photo...
I have to make sure I don't annoy you too much, ▲小早川＊▲...
I wonder if this is how it should be？
Anyway, let's keep on taking pictures.
Your serious expression is a little interesting.
Ah... Geez, it's not possible anymore.
You don't have to look at me like that.
What are you staring at？ You're an idiot...
If you do it again, I'll kick you.
Geez... That's all I can think about...
Honestly... you can be proud of it...
Hmm？ Did Rinko do anything wrong？
Not really, I don't feel good about it...
What do you want to shoot？
Heh, you say the nicest things.
No... what if I said that？ Hehe.
What！？ Why do you have to surprise me...
Oh... hey, why is the wind blowing？ Is something open？
I'll be mad if you took pictures now, okay？ I'll definitely check it later.
What are you filming？ Of course it's no good.
If you're going to shoot something like that, you better stop, okay？
Honestly... I don't know where you're shooting.
Do you really want to take photos of that kind...？
Hmm？ What did you just shoot？
